{"tid":1577942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】連登仔Fact Check完未？","createTime":"2019-09-18T02:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T05:02:50.000Z","uid":93536,"like":28,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"17982c99a8f3e2bacb503002caf5ebc61d401e12","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:46:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">過份Fact Check只會成為對家武器</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n證據分兩種:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1) 直接證據</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n- 指直接證明待證事實之證據<br />\n- 無須經過邏輯、論證、推理的過程，就可以直接認定事實<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2) 間接證據</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n- 指必須<span style=\"color: red;\">經過推理的作用論證</span>，才能間接證明事實的證據<br />\n- 必須<span style=\"color: red;\">有可資推斷的依據</span>，具有相當之蓋然性，不可憑空主觀推想或臆測<br />\n- 必須與待證事實間具有<span style=\"color: red;\">相連關係</span>，始得據以推理<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">由新屋嶺輪姦酷刑事件，到831恐怖襲擊，到被自殺潮，好多事情根本有哂間接證據，<span style=\"color: red;\">有齊警方作案動機同案件疑點。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如新屋嶺輪姦，間接證據如下:<br />\n<br />\n- 無CCTV，唔比太平紳士、記者入內，加上警員專業、情緒明顯有問題 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>(環境證據)</strong></span><br />\n- 有不止一位社工稱有接到相關Case <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>(二手證據)</strong></span><br />\n- 有見證者一手資料證實酷刑，而暴力係永遠伴隨性 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">(合理推斷)</span></strong><br />\n- 警方親口講「OT咁耐想攪你地好正常」<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">(作案動機)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">然後見到好多Fact Check撚不斷要求拎到直接證據否則當件事流料，點呀即係要受害者本人/家屬企出黎指證？要社工指名道姓公開受害者個Case？定要班狗企出黎認罪？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">事實係我地圍內根本無能力拎到直接證據，如果有齊間接證據都依然不斷Fact Check，最後只會引致一個下場，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係推翻所有間接證據！一切無從考證！</span></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以各位手足，我地要做既，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係揾齊間接證據，再去迫對家提供直接證據去釋疑！而唔係圍爐Fact Check推翻自己！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"1201317b0a4eb962a27c99b5defd6108c9735659","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"自推十年"},{"pid":"19a6915f367c9251ed88275cf6bc64dcb7844287","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"201aacb168922a949b04eab48ca3be2e03b5aea4","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"329022a0555e0f592852ec314084cc29f59ce6f5","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:48:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0c23b5a2c2d783ca36e2a0ef3a8869bd569c8734","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3f053e21298fa859f2fc292bea363ad50bd8cdc4","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f8426719c7260829b5c166ff10010d4af5f35b51","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"8084a25d4e1ce55ded0fa2f86be66905a30de1e6","tid":1577942,"uid":120480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:48:52.000Z","msg":"傾認真野，唔好再fakenews la"},{"pid":"cd32798b9ffb69806c1c47bf38ef234889ac09a1","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:48:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f38564d0d0f66c09a1944537dff4be7e13a8be02","tid":1577942,"uid":56688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"cdec3505a8c54d1098a7b0394ef5af13036be09f","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"26e73267e1cd134e17aafa7aca39e381ca7b1802","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4ab987f73d205ed285bf441633f8ba7470dd466b","tid":1577942,"uid":4156,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"打咁大篇野原來廢既"},{"pid":"931dcaef7623c55a08a2c7965975351003099a19","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>天滅中共，全黨死清光</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e7d2bb4389a092c049de7e5463edec298a1c6381","tid":1577942,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ab987f73d205ed285bf441633f8ba7470dd466b","tid":1577942,"uid":4156,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"打咁大篇野原來廢既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"點廢法，求指教"},{"pid":"f35801d0cf67b90081ba8d9f16a567eefc2bf220","tid":1577942,"uid":232817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔FACT CHECK =/= 可以FAKE NEWS</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家好多人根本分唔清間接證據同FAKE NEWS嘅分別，<br />\n前排就係有一鼓鼓吹唔洗fact check嘅風氣導致大一堆fake news出現，<br />\n代價太大，所以應該繼續FC"},{"pid":"975a04043ef99957ba794938856549b201198dc7","tid":1577942,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"一向都係大膽